WEBVTT

00:08:59.382 --> 00:09:04.151
They got up 40 minutes later every day.

00:09:04.175 --> 00:09:06.358
And they were on dad's work schedule.

00:09:06.382 --> 00:09:10.357
So they lived on Mars time for a month
and had these great adventures,

00:09:10.381 --> 00:09:12.478
like going bowling
in the middle of the night

00:09:12.502 --> 00:09:13.820
or going to the beach.

00:09:14.149 --> 00:09:17.508
And one of the things
that we all discovered

00:09:17.532 --> 00:09:21.520
is you can get anywhere in Los Angeles

00:09:21.544 --> 00:09:25.097
at 3:00 in the morning
when there's no traffic.

00:09:25.121 --> 00:09:26.595
(Laughter)

00:09:26.619 --> 00:09:27.811
So we would get off work,

00:09:27.835 --> 00:09:30.950
and we didn't want to go home
and bother our families,